caption: Sempé is one of my favorite caricaturists. I’m happy to see his art on this scale. I hope Paris will add more fresques of different artists on its walls.

Appearing, if I remember correctly, in February 2019, this fresco by (Jean-Jacques) Sempé takes, so to speak, a particular “relief” on this day. The works of this humble and human artist have accompanied us for a long time; they will undoubtedly continue.
Illustrations of the works of French illustrator Jean-Jacques Sempé
